```bash
cd ${superset_env}
pip install -r requirements.txt
. bin/activate

cd : ${superset_source}
```bash
cd ${superset_source}
cd superset/static/assets
npm install
npm run prod
cd ${superset_source}
export PYTHONPATH=.:${PYTHONPATH}

------------
```bash
cd ${superset_source}
superset/bin/superset runserver -p 12306

```bash
cd ${superset_source}
. ${superset_env}/bin/activate
export PYTHONPATH=.:${PYTHONPATH}
